![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/443435ad-3220-4d75-8704-2f0a4bbafae2/20240809_171001.jpg)

Cody Rhodes opens the show saying he wants to choose his next contender. He's interrupted by Solo Sikoa and the Bloodline.

Tonga Loa now has the Tag Team Championship and Cody Rhodes tells Solo Sikoa that he's the reason Jacob Fatu got hurt.

The Bloodline are gonna jump him but Kevin Owens comes out to even the odds. Solo says he'll deal with them when he finds Roman Reigns.

Cody tells Kevin Owens that he wants to give him a WWE Championship match.

But Kevin Owens does NOT want it. He wants to earn it. Cody Rhodes forces the Championship match on Kevin Owens anyway, against his will?

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/057b87fd-0a7e-47be-9e2c-b8eb4f2e0b12/20240809_171407.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/fd83ebb7-d115-49e0-bbee-2668804f4c5d/20240809_173515.jpg)

*   ## **_WWE TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIP NUMBER ONE CONTENDERS MATCH: STREET PROFITS DEF. A TOWN DOWN UNDER_**
    

Street Profits earn a shot at the Bloodline and the WWE Tag Team Championships

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2681dc30-b409-4e21-8eaf-3af55ca3fa6f/20240809_173501.jpg)

Cody Rhodes talks to Nick Aldis about Kevin Owens prospective WWE Championship match. Aldis says he was actually waiting for Roman to arrive before discussing a WWE Championship match.

The name Roman Reigns triggers Kevin Owens. He eventually reluctantly accepts the WWE Championship match for Bash at Berlin but Owens is NOT happy.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b610a25d-46fd-49bc-95e2-48f075be55bb/20240809_175617.jpg)

*   ## **_JADE CARGILL DEF. ALBA FYRE_**
    

Blair Davenport runs out to help the Unholy Union jump Jade and Bianca. Naomi’s music hits and the Big 3 are reunited.

